Package eu.geclipse.ui.properties

Interface Summary
IPropertiesFactory Factory, which creates and returns AbstractPropertySource objects, for object
IProperty<ESourceType> Property shown in Properties view
 

Class Summary
AbstractProperty<ESourceType> Abstract class for read-only property
AbstractPropertySource<ESourceType> This class creates array of properties for any object of type ESourceType Here list of IProperty objects are connected with instance of ESourceType If AbstractPropertySource.sourceObject contains also properties defined in another class inherited from AbstractPropertySource, then just add these properties using AbstractPropertySource.addChildSource(AbstractPropertySource)
ConnectionPropertySource Properties for IGridConnection
FileInfoSource Property source for IFileInfo
GridConnectionElementSource Property source for IGridConnectionElement
GridJobDescSource Properties for IGridJobDescription
GridJobSource Property source for IGridJob
GridProjectSource Properties for IGridProject
MultilineProperty<ESourceType> Property, which shown first line of muliline String finished by "..." If user click on button near the "...", then dialog is shown with all lines for property-value
PropertiesAdapterFactory Adapter factory for properties Register here new class inheriting AbstractPropertySource
PropertiesFactory  
PropertyId<ESourceType> Help class allow to detect which AbstractPropertySource and IProperty should return property-value
URIPropertySource Properties for URI
